        "notable": false
      },
      {
        "id": "ep-guide-S2E07-6",
        "pos": 6,
        "offset_sec": 47,
        "offset_inferred": false,
        "type": "chat",
        "actor": "steve",
        "metadata": null,
        "content": "Alright.",
        "notable": false
      },
      {
        "id": "ep-guide-S2E07-7",
        "pos": 7,
        "offset_sec": 48,
        "offset_inferred": false,
        "type": "chat",
        "actor": "",
        "metadata": null,
        "content": "Intro music",
        "notable": false
      },
      {
        "id": "ep-guide-S2E07-8",
        "pos": 8,
        "offset_sec": 52,
        "offset_inferred": false,
        "type": "chat",
        "actor": "karl",
        "metadata": null,
        "content": "So Red Nose day, Comic Relief has come round again.",
        "notable": false
      },
      {
        "id": "ep-guide-S2E07-9",
        "pos": 9,
        "offset_sec": 57,
        "offset_inferred": false,
        "type": "chat",
        "actor": "ricky",
        "metadata": null,
        "content": "Yeah. Red Nose Day is obviously the very specific date in the calendar for the whole generic term, comic relief, I think.",
        "notable": false
      },
      {
        "id": "ep-guide-S2E07-10",
        "pos": 10,
        "offset_sec": 65,
        "offset_inferred": false,
        "type": "chat",
        "actor": "steve",
        "metadata": null,
        "content": "It's normally when the telecast happens, people know that that's the day when they can dress up, do charitable acts. But of course, Comic Relief is a charity that's working all the time for disenfranchised all over the world.",
        "notable": false
      },
      {
        "id": "ep-guide-S2E07-11",
        "pos": 11,
        "offset_sec": 79,
        "offset_inferred": false,
        "type": "chat",
        "actor": "ricky",
        "metadata": null,
        "content": "And you can go to the website all year round, which is ComicRelief dot com.",
        "notable": false
      },
      {
        "id": "ep-guide-S2E07-12",
        "pos": 12,
        "offset_sec": 84,
        "offset_inferred": false,
        "type": "chat",
        "actor": "steve",
        "metadata": null,
        "content": "I think there's also RedNoseDay dot com, which is if you particularly want to donate for this year's appeal. Have you always been a strong champion of comic relief, Karl?",
        "notable": false
      },
      {
        "id": "ep-guide-S2E07-13",
        "pos": 13,
        "offset_sec": 94,
        "offset_inferred": false,
        "type": "chat",
        "actor": "karl",
        "metadata": null,
        "content": "Not really.",
        "notable": false
      },
      {
        "id": "ep-guide-S2E07-14",
        "pos": 14,
        "offset_sec": 95,
        "offset_inferred": true,
        "type": "chat",
        "actor": "",
        "metadata": null,
        "content": "Steve and Ricky laugh silently",
        "notable": false
      },
      {
        "id": "ep-guide-S2E07-15",
        "pos": 15,
        "offset_sec": 97,
        "offset_inferred": false,
        "type": "chat",
        "actor": "steve",
        "metadata": null,
        "content": "Why was I expecting that answer?",
        "notable": false
      },
      {
        "id": "ep-guide-S2E07-16",
        "pos": 16,
        "offset_sec": 100,
        "offset_inferred": false,
        "type": "chat",
        "actor": "ricky",
        "metadata": null,
        "content": "But we're doing a bit of charity now. We're donating our time. It's not much, it's not costing anything.",
        "notable": false
      },
      {
        "id": "ep-guide-S2E07-17",
        "pos": 17,
        "offset_sec": 105,
        "offset_inferred": false,
        "type": "chat",
        "actor": "karl",
        "metadata": null,
        "content": "But I do loads of stuff without going on about it. I don't think you should shout about how much you did for charity, because then who you're doing it for.",
        "notable": false
      },
      {
        "id": "ep-guide-S2E07-18",
        "pos": 18,
        "offset_sec": 111,
        "offset_inferred": false,
        "type": "chat",
        "actor": "ricky",
        "metadata": null,
        "content": "Oh, exactly. I mean, well, this is my thing, isn't it? That there's a lot of people that only do it if it's in the public eye. It's to do it really to be a busy body or to show off or to feel good about themselves. And I suppose that's good and bad. I mean, if it gets you involved, if it does some good.",
        "notable": false
      },
      {
        "id": "ep-guide-S2E07-19",
        "pos": 19,
        "offset_sec": 127,
        "offset_inferred": true,
        "type": "chat",
        "actor": "ricky",
        "metadata": null,
        "content": "My gift to the world has been you, Karl. To be quite honest. I feel that you're the world's now.",
        "notable": false
      },
      {
        "id": "ep-guide-S2E07-20",
        "pos": 20,
        "offset_sec": 132,
        "offset_inferred": false,
        "type": "chat",
        "actor": "steve",
        "metadata": null,
        "content": "I'm sure there's people in Africa going 'We'd prefer blankets!\"",
        "notable": false
      },
      {
        "id": "ep-guide-S2E07-21",
        "pos": 21,
        "offset_sec": 140,
        "offset_inferred": true,
        "type": "chat",
        "actor": "",
        "metadata": null,
        "content": "Ricky laughs",
        "notable": false
      },
      {
        "id": "ep-guide-S2E07-22",
        "pos": 22,
        "offset_sec": 141,
        "offset_inferred": true,
        "type": "chat",
        "actor": "ricky",
        "metadata": null,
        "content": "Yeah",
        "notable": false
      },
      {
        "id": "ep-guide-S2E07-23",
        "pos": 23,
        "offset_sec": 141,
        "offset_inferred": false,
        "type": "chat",
        "actor": "karl",
        "metadata": null,
        "content": "Doing a will is charity, isn't it?",
        "notable": false
      },
      {
        "id": "ep-guide-S2E07-24",
        "pos": 24,
        "offset_sec": 144,
        "offset_inferred": false,
        "type": "chat",
        "actor": "steve",
        "metadata": null,
        "content": "Is it?",
        "notable": false
      },
      {
        "id": "ep-guide-S2E07-25",
        "pos": 25,
        "offset_sec": 145,
        "offset_inferred": false,
        "type": "chat",
        "actor": "ricky",
        "metadata": null,
        "content": "Sort of.",
        "notable": false
      },
      {
        "id": "ep-guide-S2E07-26",
        "pos": 26,
        "offset_sec": 146,
        "offset_inferred": true,
        "type": "chat",
        "actor": "karl",
        "metadata": null,
        "content": "No, it is.",
        "notable": false
      },
      {
        "id": "ep-guide-S2E07-27",
        "pos": 27,
        "offset_sec": 146,
        "offset_inferred": true,
        "type": "chat",
        "actor": "steve",
        "metadata": null,
        "content": "I mean, if you make a donation to a charity within the will, I suppose that's quite charitable. But just giving money to your relatives isn't, is it?",
        "notable": false
      },
      {
        "id": "ep-guide-S2E07-28",
        "pos": 28,
        "offset_sec": 153,
        "offset_inferred": false,
        "type": "chat",
        "actor": "karl",
        "metadata": null,
        "content": "Of course it is. Well, they shouldn't have it.",
        "notable": false
      },
      {
        "id": "ep-guide-S2E07-29",
        "pos": 29,
        "offset_sec": 155,
        "offset_inferred": false,
        "type": "chat",
        "actor": "ricky",
        "metadata": null,
        "content": "They're getting somewhat for nothing, but... I don't know. It's giving something away that you have no use for.",
        "notable": false
      },
      {
        "id": "ep-guide-S2E07-30",
        "pos": 30,
        "offset_sec": 162,
        "offset_inferred": false,
        "type": "chat",
        "actor": "steve",
        "metadata": null,
        "content": "Exactly!",
        "notable": false
      },
      {
        "id": "ep-guide-S2E07-31",
        "pos": 31,
        "offset_sec": 164,
        "offset_inferred": false,
        "type": "chat",
        "actor": "karl",
        "metadata": null,
        "content": "Yeah, but forget that. It's \"someone is getting something when they've done nothing for it\" really.",
        "notable": false
      },
      {
        "id": "ep-guide-S2E07-32",
        "pos": 32,
        "offset_sec": 169,
        "offset_inferred": false,
        "type": "chat",
        "actor": "ricky",
        "metadata": null,
        "content": "Well, I suppose it is charity, but charity is usually infused with some sort of altruism. It's usually to do with them giving a piece of something that is kindly because you could do with it. Not strictly. I think you can give away something you don't need. But it's hardly donating a kidney, is it? Or some of your wages. It's like, it's not charity on your part because you're literally not around anymore. So it's no longer you giving it.",
        "notable": false
      },
